"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Install MetaMask wallet:\\n\\n[https://metamask.io/](https://metamask.io/)\\n\\nIt’s a Chrome extension and a phone app.\\nGet both.\\n\\nOpen it on one device and create a new wallet.\\n\\n\\n*************************************************\\n\\n```\\n\\t\\t     THIS IS VERY IMPORTANT\\n```\\n\\n\\n*************************************************\\n\\nMetaMask is going to give you a 12 word Recovery Seed Phrase. This is the only password you have in Web 3 and you should guard it with your life. \\n\\nTake this **VERY** **SERIOUSLY**.\\n\\n**NEVER** ever screen shot or take a picture this phrase.\\n\\n**NEVER** let these words touch the internet.\\n\\nWrite it down on paper, in multiple safe locations.\\n\\nMemorize it if you can.\\n\\nAnyone who has these words owns your wallet.\\n\\nOnce you're set up in MetaMask on one device go to the other, open MetaMask and choose \\\"Import Wallet Using Seed Phrase.\\\"\\n\\nType your 12 words into that and you will now have the same wallet on each device.\\n\\nWhen you encounter Web3 sites it will ask to connect your wallet.  This is how you “log in.”\",\"timestamp\":1634044022,\"title\":\"Welcome to Web 3.  Start Here:\"},\"digest\":\"YyEZZfS_dTLePnVpEf6efLvyKGZ8eCoZscckxVHmARQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5881D072769BE1546537bc9bF5263368276E888f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"j2NHTmwjN7nQ_6e1htR2nCoj5FMKe5UlQZbfXFEVH4Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rJHl2aPPpmK8dxA09fD1IZLOMC1OlXVQsvKL4wvx5sA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"H7ACkWjlTHfjtZHmFzH7W3r9_W_gFE1CSy1N4d2jXh31c9gH218xOgb0rHlT7pOGPH8OTTtY6B1f2MPyG0HwHg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1b17c7e78d1d446169e309bd1d8b12ece60aeaa17b68767e1c499a0c249860902580c51374aa1917aa47ed215dde02a4b9e8eecba49d36b750c63ff7d84b5c961c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_op